    matrix.factory  

    • Uses of FactoryMatrix in matrix.factory

      Classes in matrix.factory that implement FactoryMatrix 
      Modifier and Type Class and Description
      class  FactoryMatrixDefault
      Creates matrix with a dense implementation of float[][].
      class  FactoryMatrixSparse
      This class constructs matrices representation given by a HashMap.
      class  FactoryMatrixSparseHash
      This class creates matrices represented as HashMap> The first map represents the rows, while the second contains the values for a column in a given row.
      class  FactoryMatrixSparseHashPar
      The matrix constructed by this factory is a subclass of the matrix created by FactoryMatrixSparseHash.
      class  FactoryMatrixThreshold
      This class creates a matrix that dynamically changes it representation between MatrixFloat and MatrixSparseHash
      class  FactoryMatrixTrove
      This class creates matrices represented as TIntObjectHashMap.
      class  FactoryMatrixTrovePar
      The matrix constructed by this factory is a subclass of the matrix created by FactoryMatrixTrove.
